在 Massive Attack 的支持下，已有 100 多个艺人退出了 2024 年加沙大逃亡抵制活动https://www.nme.com/news/music/over-100-acts-have-now-dropped-out-of-the-great-escape-2024-in-gaza-boycott-with-support-from-大规模攻击-3756090？utm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign =超过100个行为现在已经放弃了2024年大逃亡，在加沙抵制，并有来自大规模的支持攻击Tom SkinnerTue, 14 May 2024 14:13:42 +0000 Music NewsNewsNME RadarIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3756090 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Massive Attack 乐队的 Robert &quot;3D&quot; Del Naja（左）和 Alfie Templeman（右）在舞台上现场表演的两张并排照片" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>阿尔菲·坦普尔曼说：“我的道德不能也不会与娱乐和人类苦难的融合相一致。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/over-100-acts-have-now-dropped-out-of-the-great-escape-2024-in-gaza-boycott-with-support-from-massive-attack-3756090">在 Massive Attack 的支持下，超过 100 名艺人已退出《2024 年加沙大逃亡》抵制活动，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Massive Attack 乐队的 Robert &quot;3D&quot; Del Naja（左）和 Alfie Templeman（右）在舞台上现场表演的两张并排照片" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AlfieTempleman-Massive-Attack-The-Great-Escape-Festival-boycott-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>为了声援巴勒斯坦，已有超过 100 名艺人退出今年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/the-great-escape">大逃亡音乐节</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/massive-attack">Massive Attack</a>也公开支持抵制活动。</p><p> 2024 年的该活动将展示新晋艺术家，将于明天（5 月 15 日）至周六（18 日）在布莱顿的各个音乐场馆举行。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-listid="71"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/the-10-best-new-artists-the-great-escape-2023-radar-3443679"><b>我们在 2023 年大逃亡中看到的 10 个最佳新表演</b></a></li></ul><p>“大逃亡”由巴克莱银行赞助，由于该银行对向以色列供应武器的公司进行金融投资，巴克莱银行在加沙持续冲突中一直引起争议。</p><p>这个问题首先在发起人 How To Catch A Pig 和 The Menstrual Cramps 乐队发起的请愿书中得到强调，此后签名的音乐家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lambrini-girls">Lambrini Girls</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alfie-templeman">Alfie Templeman</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lip-critic">Lip Critic</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mary-in-the-junkyard">Mary In The Junkyard</a> 。所有这些人都敦促电影节放弃巴克莱银行的赞助商。</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cherym-pull-out-of-the-great-escape-festival-due-to-its-links-with-barclays-bank-3617202">由于音乐节与巴克莱银行的联系，Cherym 退出了 The Great Escape</a> ，之后唱片公司<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cherym-pull-out-of-the-great-escape-festival-due-to-its-links-with-barclays-bank-3617202">Alcopop 和 Big Scary Monsters 也</a>加入了抵制并退出了该活动。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dozens-more-artists-join-great-escape-2024-boycott-as-half-the-line-up-demands-festival-drop-barclays-sponsor-in-solidarity-with-palestine-3619074">很快，又有数十个表演团体纷纷效仿</a>，其中超过一半的表演团体要求 The Great Escape 放弃对巴克莱银行的赞助。</p><p>在谈到不参加音乐节的决定时，兰布里尼女孩表示：“我们今年不会参加大逃亡音乐节。考虑到巴克莱的赞助，这是一种有针对性的文化抵制方式。</p><p> “巴克莱银行向向以色列国防军提供军事技术和武器的公司提供超过 10 亿英镑的金融服务，从而使加沙地带的恐怖现象长期存在。”</p><p>现在，共有 106 名艺术家取消了原定在 2024 年大逃亡中的演出，约占全部节目的四分之一。根据一份新闻稿，他们将电影节与巴克莱银行的合作伙伴关系“资助种族灭绝”作为退出的理由。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C66pOrgteOZ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50p